+## watch mobile-share
+
+Watches a phone/sync share folder and imports new files only once.
+
+Scan once and exit:
+
+```text
+python pala.py watch mobile-share "C:\Users\you\Google Drive\ChatGPT Shares" --once
+```
+
+Continuous watch:
+
+```text
+python pala.py watch mobile-share "C:\Users\you\Google Drive\ChatGPT Shares" --interval 30
+```
+
+Useful options:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--once` | Run one scan and exit |
+| `--interval 30` | Seconds between scans |
+| `--project trugurpala/pala-memory-core` | Link imported records to a project |
+| `--tag mobile` | Add an extra tag |
+| `--max-records 25` | Limit text records per imported file |
+| `--max-chars 12000` | Limit text stored per record |
+
 ## capture browser
 
 Captures a public or local URL into a memory record.
