+## Mobile Share Watch Behavior
+
+The watcher scans a shared folder and imports only files it has not seen before. It stores its state under `data/inbox/`.
+
+| Mode | Behavior |
+|---|---|
+| `--once` | Scan one time and exit |
+| `--interval <seconds>` | Keep scanning until stopped |
+| state file | Prevents importing the same file repeatedly |
+
 ## Design Rule
 
 If a connector is fragile, keep it optional. The core should still work through manual capture and file import.
