+# v0.9 Mobile Share Watch
+
+Date: 2026-06-09
+Phase: mobile share watcher preview
+Status: PASS for mobile share watcher preview
+
+## Goal
+
+Watch a phone/sync share folder and import new files without repeatedly importing files that were already processed.
+
+## Added Behavior
+
+| Area | Change |
+|---|---|
+| CLI | Added `python pala.py watch mobile-share <path>` |
+| One-shot mode | `--once` scans and exits |
+| Continuous mode | `--interval <seconds>` scans until stopped |
+| State | Seen file fingerprints are stored under `data/inbox/` |
+| Import path | Reuses `import mobile-share` behavior |
+
+## Command
+
+```powershell
+python .\pala.py watch mobile-share .\data\inbox\mobile-watch-smoke --once --project trugurpala/pala-memory-core --tag smoke-test
+```
+
+## Expected Result
+
+```text
+watching <path>
+imported <n> text record(s) and <m> attachment file(s) from <file>
+watch scan complete processed=<count> seen=<count>
+```
+
+## Smoke Test
+
+Created a watched folder with one text note and one PNG-like attachment, then ran the watcher twice:
+
+```powershell
+python .\pala.py watch mobile-share .\data\inbox\mobile-watch-smoke --once --project trugurpala/pala-memory-core --tag smoke-test --max-records 5 --max-chars 2000
+python .\pala.py watch mobile-share .\data\inbox\mobile-watch-smoke --once --project trugurpala/pala-memory-core --tag smoke-test --max-records 5 --max-chars 2000
+python .\pala.py brief today
+python .\pala.py dashboard export
+```
+
+Observed output:
+
+```text
+watch scan complete processed=2 seen=2
+watch scan complete processed=0 seen=2
+brief saved data\reports\2026-06-09-brief.md
+dashboard data saved dashboard\records.json
+```
+
+## Release Posture
+
+This is a folder watcher preview. It does not monitor phone OS events directly; it watches a local/synced folder.
